{"tid":755212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"直擊！美心流心月餅券開賣即斷市 水客貨即場收券","createTime":"2018-07-25T04:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T11:56:45.000Z","uid":39464,"like":24,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"a0352ccb8c52e3d679f9b721e599451873768788","tid":755212,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180725/large/1532492434_ffb3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180725%2Flarge%2F1532492434_ffb3.png&h=873bf972&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180725/large/1532492048_735e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180725%2Flarge%2F1532492048_735e.jpg&h=ecda1e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n排隊期間有市民因為插隊問題爆衝突。王心義攝(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180725/large/1532492019_d645.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180725%2Flarge%2F1532492019_d645.png&h=8d5a3630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批市民搶購月餅券，原價228元一張計算，即場轉售5張最多可賺160元。王心義攝(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180725/large/1532492014_ad28.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180725%2Flarge%2F1532492014_ad28.png&h=eedfc022&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n職員提前派籌阻止有人繼續打尖。潘柏林攝(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180725/large/1532492018_404e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180725%2Flarge%2F1532492018_404e.png&h=704ab110&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n淘寶網上已有人聲稱可代購美心流心月餅券。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180725/large/1532492016_965f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180725%2Flarge%2F1532492016_965f.png&h=d5d29340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180725/large/1532492023_27b1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180725%2Flarge%2F1532492023_27b1.png&h=31af3f92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網民聲稱有騙子借代買月餅券騙財。"},{"pid":"870a468695ae332c5bfa4bd1537b4ace979d6f9d","tid":755212,"uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:37:26.000Z","msg":"中秋未到，月餅券炒風再起。連鎖快餐店美心今日開售「流心奶黃月餅券」，上水新都廣場分店早上吸引約200人排隊搶購。排頭位的葉小姐稱凌晨4點多已到場，但強調不是炒賣用。店舖早上7點半開門，每人限購5張，美心起初無安排派籌，但後來有市民因「打尖」問題互相以粗口對罵，甚至推撞，美心急急派籌杜絕打券，所有月餅券在早上10時已售罄，美心稱要到8月1日再開售。<br />\n<br />\n記者現場所見，最少有3名水貨客在店外收購月餅券，既有操普通話、亦有操廣東話，收購價由240至260元一張不等。以原價228元一張計算，轉售5張最多可賺160元。<br />\n<br />\n網上就有facebook專頁以每張250元收購，聲稱首批收購1萬張；亦有專頁聲稱出售流心奶皇月餅券，每張310元，較原價高35%。而淘寶網已有代購流心奶皇月餅券，價格高達333元，較原價高46%。去年美心已經每人限買10張流心奶皇月餅券，今年削減至每人限買5張。<br />\n<br />\n排隊買餅券的港人陳先生直指人龍超乎預期，料部份人是為了炒賣。內地人黃先生稱流心奶黃月餅在內地很受歡迎，自己計劃買10多盒贈送親友，又稱沒有想過買月餅也很難。有排隊的上水居民稱，去年幫內地親友買20盒奶黃月餅，在內地經商亦特別喜歡送奶黃月餅，而一般內地人較多買香港的雙黃白蓮蓉月餅。<br />\n<br />\n月餅券炒風四起，但有港人在交易網站發文投訴有賣家要求轉賬一半金額作訂金，其後要求再轉賬餘下尾數，當照數支付後，賣家便人間蒸發。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180725/58483431\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180725%2F58483431&d=6VBb3GZXc6PsEmgOQRdGZ%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=30234bf4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180725%2F58483431&h=6f0a7d58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180725/58483431</a>"},{"pid":"251dab6b55faa8c52b2b3649811ae76e37b43949","tid":755212,"uid":10680,"like":105,"dislike":1,"score":104,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:38:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2bdc1825f8e2edae630db3208f626b23f073e2f6","tid":755212,"uid":46192,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:40:17.000Z","msg":"食左識飛?"},{"pid":"203430615c4816ef534fac89a5773197a2db4112","tid":755212,"uid":18012,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2bdc1825f8e2edae630db3208f626b23f073e2f6","tid":755212,"uid":46192,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:40:17.000Z","msg":"食左識飛?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:43:14.000Z","msg":"飛上月球"},{"pid":"820defa6ed07a58ea51be646e42da946b5263971","tid":755212,"uid":39628,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:45:01.000Z","msg":"又係蝗虫搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99760620647c106d8e8dde0ebef157f7f99ca293","tid":755212,"uid":52595,"like":82,"dislike":2,"score":80,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:50:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eefb91cf4717fe0431cd1479f77eba9671223cd5","tid":755212,"uid":51127,"like":40,"dislike":4,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:50:47.000Z","msg":"美心店員自己收起曬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實好垃圾，唔明有乜好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f589c6cef213a87627afdd03da5690b9833660bd","tid":755212,"uid":52595,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:51:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2788ec2f90eb857bce28fd9f81af3dba539c9676","tid":755212,"uid":49643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eefb91cf4717fe0431cd1479f77eba9671223cd5","tid":755212,"uid":51127,"like":40,"dislike":4,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:50:47.000Z","msg":"美心店員自己收起曬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"h